ek to collaborate with member companies on specific projects upcoming events may 07 supri b annual meeting may 7th 8th 2012 jul 16 reservoir simulation shortcourse july 16 20 2012 2012 summer short course fundamentals of reservoir simulation instructors khalid aziz lou durlofsky & hamdi tchelepi this course will cover both fundamentals and selected advanced topics in reservoir simulation view event calendar helpful links research faculty research areas affiliate resources related courses related resources hartley conference center health and safety computers resources room resources how can we help maps & directions stanfordwho office of the registrar contact us connect to earth sciences facebook itunes u twitter youtube
